title: Mid-size luxury vehicles : sales by model in the United States 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart shows Sales in units on the Y-axis for 17 different Models for 2 groups 2019, and 2018 that are presented on the X-axis.
Model Tesla Model 3 had the maximum Sales in units among all 2 groups, and it was for 2019. The minimum Sales in units was observed in Model Acura RLX for 2019.
The maximum Sales in units for 2019 that was found in Model Tesla Model 3 was 158.1 times larger than the minimum Sales in units observed in Model Acura RLX.
On average, the Model Tesla Model 3 had the highest Sales in units for all 2 groups 2019, and 2018. Whereas Acura RLX had the lowest average Sales in units.
